				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%B1u-vu-Vi-x%E1%BB%A9-ng%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-%E1%BA%A4p-t%E1%BB%AB-o%E1%BA%A3n/poem-yk3qRVhm2HgmzNvB8i8wgg">Hựu vu Vi xứ ngật Đại Ấp từ oản - 又于韋處乞大邑瓷碗</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/Kh%C3%A1ch-ho%C3%A0i/poem-2-LyHF-GcySUvfgsf8YIbQ">Khách hoài - 客懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/author-HrCILDC9soRz0JVGAcDF9w">Lê Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Minh-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tr%C3%B9ng-c%E1%BB%ADu-di%E1%BB%87c-d%C4%A9-b%E1%BB%87nh-b%E1%BA%A5t-ph%C3%B3-Thu%E1%BA%ADt-C%E1%BB%95-h%E1%BB%99i-t%C3%A1i-d%E1%BB%A5ng-ti%E1%BB%81n-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-z1KeYwsg-Ky1cHO-w8Y1Ng">Minh nhật trùng cửu diệc dĩ bệnh bất phó Thuật Cổ hội tái dụng tiền vận - 明日重九亦以病不赴述古會再用前韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-%C4%91%E1%BB%9Bi-sinh-ca/poem-XGDV-KqgVFWcId2MqnewVg">Ngọc đới sinh ca - 玉帶生歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/author-edTceA8S1YU0BsK54Tjq9Q">Chu Di Tôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%C3%A1ng-hoa-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-gA5JJaf5Xy6SshvZx4FFWg">Táng hoa từ - 葬花詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/T%E1%BA%B7ng-B%E1%BB%93ng-T%E1%BB%AD/poem-Ohoz96nNj3k1Fia7TW3_HQ">Tặng Bồng Tử - 贈蓬子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Nhu%E1%BA%ADn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-R7ErFLEFODN8ooTxAYHrdQ">Tây Hồ trúc chi từ kỳ 5 - 西湖竹枝詞其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Nhu%E1%BA%ADn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-Ic-wM4uTt21tJ0mNZjugOA">Thi Nhuận Chương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thi%C3%AAn-D%E1%BB%A5c-phi%C3%AAu-k%E1%BB%B5-ca/poem-4H7cidyLDPJCsh696qWFuQ">Thiên Dục phiêu kỵ ca - 天育驃騎歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/T%E1%BB%91ng-M%C3%A3-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i-l%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-quy-Giang-Nam/poem-Hmh6ia55o5XIJ1ap916okg">Tống Mã tú tài lạc đệ quy Giang Nam - 送馬秀才落第歸江南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/author-tOqeEdGQ0OZRwfU1Vi35GA">Lưu Trường Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/T%E1%BB%B1-qu%C3%A2n-chi-xu%E1%BA%A5t-h%E1%BB%B9-k%E1%BB%B3-07/poem-T95Dl2UHSYAIHcK-xJpCVg">Tự quân chi xuất hỹ kỳ 07 - 自君之出矣其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
